The ICO of InsurePal took place on January 16th in 2018. The price for one IPL token was $0.1. Total token amount is 300m where 67% were available for token crowdsale. The last third was mostly shared by the InsurePal team and their advisors. The soft cap was 5m and the hard cap 18m. They achieved 12m in the pre-sale round. The last 6m were raised in only 80 seconds. Due to this short period every participant has profited of the bonus scheme and therefore received another discount of 10%. <ref>https://icodrops.com/insurepal/, access 06/26/18.</ref>


